name: TechnoVision 2024
descreption: Annual technical symposium featuring cutting-edge technology presentations, workshops on emerging technologies, and networking opportunities for students and professionals in the field of computer science and engineering.
venue: St. Joseph's College of Engineering and Technology, Palai

name: Code Quest Championship
descreption: Competitive programming contest designed to challenge students' algorithmic thinking and coding skills. Features multiple rounds including debugging, optimization challenges, and real-world problem solving scenarios.

name: AI & Machine Learning Workshop
descreption: Comprehensive hands-on workshop covering fundamentals of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Includes practical sessions on Python libraries, neural networks, and real-world AI applications in various industries.

name: Cybersecurity Awareness Seminar
descreption: Educational seminar focusing on current cybersecurity threats, best practices for digital safety, ethical hacking concepts, and career opportunities in information security. Features industry experts and live demonstrations.

name: Web Development Bootcamp
descreption: Intensive 3-day bootcamp covering modern web development technologies including HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, React, and Node.js. Participants will build complete web applications from scratch with mentorship from industry professionals.
